This paper deals with a central problem in machine learning and pattern recognition, which is feature selection. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions practical applications in bioinformatics, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions solving a linear system using least squares and singular value decomposition, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
